\mt1 Kolosi  
\imt1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rani m…ô n…ôfe i n…ôkuku…ô  
\ip Kolosi in n…ôkuku…ô s…ô ro kahar i Pol r…®m…ôrai n…ôp…®n in ramar…ô ia kalapus fwe Rom ia n…ôp…®n riti ipaka t…® nuk 59 u…ô 60. Epafras rev…ôn fwe Rom m…®ni pen t…® Pol m…ô nahat…ôn eiku…ô me nepw…®n fwe Kolosi kamhahat…ôn n…ôrmama m…ô nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ônraha ia Kristo r…®pk…ômwhen mh…ô. Nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha hamahat…ôn ir…ôha m…ô tuh…ôfwaki m na…°elo me, mhesi pen natuak…ômien me nepw…®n, mh…ôsiai mwi n…ôp…®n ikinan me nepw…®n. Pol r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i rev…ôn t…® nir…ôha m…ô tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôr…ôr …ôknek…®n, mh…ôpw…ôh n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien ia nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha. Kristo in rasori ia narimnari me pam. Nemh…ôien s…ôv…ôi Kristo in …ôpa ruvehim…®ru k…®taha t…® noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôk…®taha. Iesu r…®fi nari ia k…®taha ts…ôpw…ôh mwi n…®siaiien natuak…ômien me s…ôv…ôi i…ôrmama.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Efes 1:1\x*Iou Pol, iou aposol riti s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôni n…ôkwan m…ô tako, m…®ne pi…ôvtaha Timoti.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Rom 1:7\x*N…ôkuku…ô i rauvehe tukumiaha n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn fwe taon n…ôha Kolosi.  
\p K…®miaha n…ô pi…ôvmaha me hi…ôm…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®miaha Kristo, hiamahat…ôt…ô p…ôrhien ir…ô.  
\p Pw…ôh Kumwes…ôn Tata s…ôk…®taha tr…ôriari pehe namasanien m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuien m k…®miaha.   
\s1 N…ô…°n…ô…°…®niien m…®ne n…ôfwakiien  
\p
\v 3 N…ôp…®n me pam, n…ôp…®n k…®maha iaham…ôfwaki tukumiaha, iaham…ôni tanak t…® Kumwes…ôn i in Tata s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha.  
\v 4 Iaham…ôni tanak tukwe in t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iah…ôuv…ôre…°i raka m…ô k…®miaha hiamahat…ôt…ô …ôknek…®n ia Iesu Kristo n…ôn…ô mamhokeikei p…®k n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn.  
\v 5 Nahat…ôt…ôien m…®ne nokeikeiien s…ôk…®miaha ro iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô hi…ôukur…ôn amasan ia rer…®miaha m…ô Kumwes…ôn truvei pehe n…ôfe nari s…ô r…®n…ôpn…ôpen…ô ir…ô m k…®miaha fwe ia neiai. Hi…ôuv…ôre…°i raka narimnari me n…ôha ia n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien, in i n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo.  
\v 6 Ia kwopun me pam ia t…ôkure t…®pr…ôn…ô n…ôrmama kamh…ôni irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kristo, n…ôn…ô rauku…ô mamo kw…ônkwan mauver…ô mamo amasan n…®m…®ruien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama me h…ôp…®k. R…ômwhen a mwi ia k…®miaha n…ôp…®n hiamre…°i mh…ôukur…ôn n…®p…ôrhienien n…ôha ia namasanien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn, n…ôn…ô rauver…ô mwi muku…ô ia n…®m…®ruien s…ôk…®miaha.  
\v 7 Epafras r…®nahat…ôn k…®miaha ia n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha. In i…ôrmama riti s…ôk…®maha iahokeikei p…®k in, iahamo tukwini p…ôri nari k…®maha min. K…®maha iah…ôukur…ôn n…ôt…®…°iteien ir…ô, ramasitu ia wok s…ôv…ôi Kristo mam…ô…°kiari tukwini s…ôk…®maha.  
\v 8 In r…®m…ôni pehe tukumaha i m…ô nokeikeiien s…ôk…®miaha rasori raku pen t…® N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan.   
\p
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Efes 1:9,16,17, Fil 1:9\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô n…ôp…®n iah…ôre…°i n…ôvisauien n…ôha, n…ôn…ô iaham…ôfwaki tukumiaha ia n…ôp…®n me pam, mamh…ôres m…ô k…®miaha tih…ôuvehe mh…ôukur…ôn amasan pam n…ôkwai Kumwes…ôn ia nukur…ônien s…ô raku pen t…® N…ôn…®mw…®n s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Fil 1:27, Efes 2:10\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô m…®ne k…®miaha tihamar…ô ia nar…ôien atukwatukw s…ô ramo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha rer…®n rama…°ien, mamh…ôuku…ô kw…ônkwamiaha ia noien amasan me pam, n…ôn…ô ia n…ôp…®n me nukur…ônien s…ôk…®miaha truvehe masori mwi hi…ôukur…ôn amasan mwi Kumwes…ôn.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Efes 1:19, 3:16\x*Iaham…ôfwaki m…ô n…®skaiien asori s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn tro k…®miaha hi…ôskai n…ôp…®n n…ôr…ôhaien truvehe, pw…ôh hi…ôrer …ôknek…®n ia n…ôp…®n me pam, n…ôn…ô mho n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha r…ôpw…ômw…®s, n…ôn…ô mamho k…®miaha hiama…°ien  
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Efes 1:11,18\x*mamh…ôni tanak t…® Tata Kumwes…ôn t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in r…®no k…®miaha m…ô hi…ôukur…ôn nuvehi p…ôriien naut…ô k…®miaha n…ôrmama ikinan me s…ôv…ônhi. In r…®n…ômri karen naut…ô n…ôha ia kwopun rukuraan ik…®n.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Luk 22:53, Efes 2:2\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in r…®peki raka k…®taha ia n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi n…ôpit…ôvien, m…®peki pen k…®taha ia n…®t…ôt…ô s…ô T…®ni keikei ram…ôr…®m…ônu ir…ô.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Efes 1:6,7\x*T…®ni r…®fi nari ia k…®taha, mo m…ô Kumwes…ôn tr…ôpw…ôh n…ôrpw…®nien noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôk…®taha.   
\s1 Kristo in rasori ia narimnari me pam  
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt 2Kor 4:4, Jon 1:18\x*T…®ni Kumwes…ôn in r…ômwhen atukwatukw ia Tata s…ôv…ônhi s…ô s…ôpk…ôtoni mh…ô. In n…ômritaik s…ô in rasori ia neiai m…®ne t…®pr…ôn…ô m…®ne narimnari me pam.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Jon 1:3,10\x*In rasori t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in r…®no pam narimnari me n…ôha, narimnari me s…ôm…ôme sam…ôtoni m…®ne s…ôm…ôme s…ôpk…ôtoni mh…ô, ki…° me, u…ô ieni m…ô, u…ô n…ôn…®mw…®n me s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôuvehi nasoriien m…®ne n…ôr…®m…ônuien. Narimnari me pam n…ôha, T…®ni Kumwes…ôn r…®no ir…ôha m…ô s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Jon 1:1, 8:58\x*In r…®m…ôkupw…ôn mar…ô ia narimnari me pam, n…ôn…ô narimnari me pam kamhar…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…®skaiien s…ôv…ônhi ram…ôkwt…ômhiri ir…ôha.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Efes 1:22-23, Wok Me 26:23, Rev 1:5\x*In rasori ia nakalasia me s…ôv…ônhi ir…ôha h…ômwhen ia n…®pwran in k…ônkapw…ô. In nukunen, i…ôrmama s…ô r…®m…ôkupw…ôn m…ôtui mwi ia nemh…ôien s…ôv…ônhi, ro pen in ramasan ia narimnari me pam mukupw…ôn.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Jon 1:16, Kol 2:9\x*Kumwes…ôn ramar…ô pam ia reri T…®ni muku…ôr ir…ô. N…ôn…ô Kumwes…ôn rer…®n ra…°ien pw…ôh ro iam…®nhi ir…ô.  
\v 20 \fig N…®te Iesu r…®n…ômri n…ôm…ôrinuien|alt="Nail pierced hands" src="HK00322B.TIF" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="Kol 1:20" \fig*\x - \xo 1:20 \xt Efes 1:10, 2:16, Rom 5:1, Efes 1:7, 2:13, 1Jon 2:2\x*Rer…®n ra…°ien r…®peki narimnari me pam ia t…ôkure t…®pr…ôn…ô m…®ne ia neiai h…ôn…ôvis…ô ir…ôha min, muvi s…®mw…®n pehe ir…ôha ia t…®ni, n…ôn…ô m…ômri n…ôm…ôrinuien ia n…®ten s…ô r…®naiu ia nei kamarkuaui.   
