\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Efes 2:14-16, Efes 5:27\x*M…ôt…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô T…®ni ruvehe i…ôrmama m…ômwhen ia k…®taha, memh…ô, ro pen Kumwes…ôn ro k…®miaha hi…ôuvehe in me nepw…®n. In ro iam…®nhi ir…ô m…ô tr…ôrpwi irapw k…®miaha ia n…ônimen hiatukwatukw pam,\f + \fr 1:22 \ft U…ô ‚Äúk…®miaha n…ôkur ikinan me s…ôv…ônhi.‚Äù\f* mh…ômher, k…ôpw…ôh n…ôtoniien noien …ôr…ôha riti s…ôk…®miaha.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Efes 3:17, Hip 3:14, Mak 16:15, 1Tim 3:16\x*M…ôt…ô tiham…ôkeikei mh…ômwur pen ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha, mamh…ôrer …ôknek…®n ir…ô, mh…ôpw…ôh n…®kiukiuien, mh…ôpw…ôh narakaien ia noien s…ô hiam…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha ia n…ô…°kiariien amasan n…ôha hi…ôuv…ôre…°i raka m…®ne n…ôfe rani. K…®n…ôvisau irapw raka n…ô…°kiariien amasan n…ôha ia kwopun me ia t…®pr…ôn…ô. Iou Pol, iou i…ôrmama riti s…ô iakamasitu ia wok n…ôha.   
