\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Efes 3:13\x*T…ôkwt…ôkwuni rer…®k ra…°ien a m…ô kamo n…ômis…ôien miou tukumiaha.\f + \fr 1:24 \ft Pol ram…ômak fwe ia kalapus n…ôp…®n r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i. Kalapus n…ôha in n…ôha n…ômis…ôien s…ô Pol ram…ô…°kiari ir…ô ia vas 24.\f* Ia n…ômis…ôien me i iakamre…°i ia n…®pwrak, iakamr…®p…®n pen a mamo sampam ia n…ômis…ôien me s…ôv…ôi Kristo s…ôm…ôme in r…®m…ôre…°i t…® n…®pwran. N…®pwran n…ô in n…ô nakalasia me s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Efes 3:2,7-8\x*Iou i…ôrmama riti s…ô iakamasitu ia nakalasia me n…ôha. Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ômri pehe wok i ia r…ô…°…®k m…ô takasitu ia k…®miaha, m…ôvisau irapw pam n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi m k…®miaha.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 1:26 \xt Rom 16:25-26, Efes 3:3-5,9-10\x*N…ô…°kiariien n…ôha in n…ô…°kiariien riti s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôrkwaf…ô t…® n…ôrmama fwe kupw…ôn, m…ôt…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni n…ôha Kumwes…ôn r…®no pui m n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 1:27 \xt Efes 1:18, 1Tim 1:1\x*Kumwes…ôn rokeikei m…ô tro n…ôrmama me n…ôha s…ôv…ônhi h…ôtoni mh…ôukur…ôn m…ô n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha in r…®n…ôrkwaf…ô i truvei pen naut…ô amasan m n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel. Naut…ô amasan n…ôha Kristo ia rer…®miaha, i…ôm…ô s…ô hiam…ôt…®…°ite ir…ô truvei pehe nasoriien m k…®miaha ia neiai.   
\p
\v 28 \x - \xo 1:28 \xt Efes 4:13\x*Kristo n…ôha, k…®maha iaham…ôni irapw in, mamh…ôv…ôha…° m n…ôrmama me pam, mamhahat…ôn n…ôrmama me pam ia nukur…ônien me pam, m…ô ir…ôha pam tuh…ôuvehe mh…ômru…ô ia noien s…ôv…ôi Kristo, n…ôn…ô iah…ôrpwi irapw ir…ôha ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 1:29 \xt Efes 3:7,20, Fil 4:13\x*Ia noien n…ôha iakam…ômwur mamsese tukwe mamesi pen n…®skaiien asori s…ôv…ôi Kristo s…ô ramo wok ia n…®m…®ruien s…ôiou.   
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 Iakokeikei m…ô tih…ôukur…ôn m…ô iou iakamsese p…®k tukumiaha n…ôkur Kolosi, m…®ne n…ôkur Laotisia, m…®ne nakalasia me pam s…ôm…ôme h…ôpk…ôtoni raka mh…ô n…ônimek ia n…ôp…®n riti.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Efes 3:4,18, Kol 1:26\x*Iakokeikei m…ô takasitu ia nir…ôha pw…ôh h…ôre…°i ramasan fwe ia rer…®nraha, mh…ôuvehe mho kuatia mhokeikei ir…ôha me, mh…ôukur…ôn amasan n…®pwrai n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien n…ôn…ô mh…ôuvehi namasanien me pam s…ôv…ôi noien i. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô ir…ôha tuh…ôukur…ôn n…®pwrai n…ô…°kiariien s…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôrkwaf…ô i fwe kupw…ôn. N…ô…°kiariien n…ôha in Kristo,  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Aes 45:3, 1Kor 1:24,30, Efes 3:19\x*i…ôm…ô s…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôrkwaf…ô pen nukur…ônien amasan me pam s…ôv…ônhi ir…ô.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Rom 16:18, Efes 5:6, Kol 2:8\x*Iakam…ô…°kiari iam…®nhi ir…ô m k…®miaha t…® n…ôsis…ô…°ien ia n…ô…°kiariien eiku…ô me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama s…ô r…ôsien mavi raka n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt 1Kor 5:3\x*N…®p…ôrhienien, n…®pwrak r…®pkar…ô mh…ô k…®miaha min, m…ôt…ô iakamar…ô k…®taha m k…®miaha ia n…ôn…®mw…®k. N…ôn…ô rer…®k ra…°ien p…®k t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iakam…ôtoni m…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha kuatia a, n…ôn…ô hiamahat…ôt…ô …ôknek…®n ia Kristo.   
\s1 N…ôrmama me s…ôv…ôi Kristo n…®m…®ruien s…ôv…ônraha ruv…ôuvehe muv…ôuku…ôr raka  
