\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Efes 2:14-16, 1Pit 2:24\x*N…ôkuku…ô n…ôha r…ôr…ôha ia k…®taha k…®m…ôrai pen noien …ôr…ôha me ir…ô s…ôk…®taha m…ô tuk…ôrpw…®n pehe m k…®taha, Kumwes…ôn ruv…ôuvehi raka raka n…ôkuku…ô n…ôha irau n…ô…°kiariien me s…ôv…ôi Loa s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôrkwi k…®taha, m…ôrui t…ôrini pen ia nei kamarkuaui. Ro pen in r…®fi nari ia k…®taha.  
